And the fanatic is always concealing a secret doubt.

788
01:16:21,650 --> 01:16:22,970
他長什麼樣
What did he look like?

789
01:16:25,730 --> 01:16:27,030
我不記得了
I can't remember.

790
01:16:49,060 --> 01:16:50,960
今天之後  彼得
After today, Peter,

791
