在操場上開著車跑  你不會朝這邊看嗎
bunch of boys flogging a car round a field?

885
01:26:57,040 --> 01:26:58,690
他是怎麼回事  他不喜歡我們嗎
What's the matter with him? Doesn't he like us?

886
